  "texts": [
    "In the available parking space prediction problem, a new dataset was also constructed.",
    "It included variables capable of providing a possible correlation with the free parking spaces variable.",
    "For this problem, three models were developed with their complexity as the main criterion.",
    "The models included a simple linear regression, a support vector machine model modified to work for regression, and a MLP.",
    "The relative absolute error (RAE) was used as an evaluation metric."
  ],
